{"tid":1754076,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要!] 義士唔係condom ! 建議籌組「補償未來基金」","createTime":"2019-11-25T05:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T04:47:04.000Z","uid":107157,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"443710a80782b497f06d184259effa7dd7df876a","tid":1754076,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:54:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">補償未來基金</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原因:</span></span><br />\n前線義士為我地不斷付出，甚至被判處10年監禁，所以想大家做啲野，回饋返佢地失去左既時間。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">方法:</span></span><br />\n工會制定一張黃色VIP卡，提供大幅度優惠比持卡人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">申請條件:</span> </span>為因革命而被判監既人士<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">有限年期: </span></span>為「被判監既時間」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">集資方式: </span></span><br />\n工會向願意参與既機構收取資金而籌備「補償未來基金」，並派發「金豬貼紙」予參與商戶。<br />\n<br />\n義士可以到有「金豬貼紙」商戶享有極高優惠既價錢消費。而大家可以多啲去金豬貼紙商戶幫襯回饋。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家文宣/推/提出更多意見!!!!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"689eced8377bc0621bbb8b0267122d6d1e570720","tid":1754076,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:58:51.000Z","msg":"唔好剩係正皮，落埋黎留個言幫推啦<br />\n<br />\n[重要!!]義士唔係condom  建議籌組「補償未來基金」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754066</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"17ddb9e8a748cf5931171d35dba7e88b73b13afa","tid":1754076,"uid":59679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"直接俾份工佢地會唔會更好"},{"pid":"f6ad1f2f1206d23b2b2fab503793